valueOf

public static KeyScope valueOf(String value)
Returns the enum constant for the enum type with the specified name. Note, scope type names are all uppercase.

Throws:
NullPointerException - if value is null.
IllegalArgumentException - if value does not the name of a declared scope type constant.
Parameters:
